# Source Discovery

{% include "runtime/partial/step_retry_context.md.j2" %}

Read only the current `input.json`, its generated row schemas, sibling `chart.schema.json`, sibling `state.sqlite3` through `brand-size-chart-source-discovery-state`, and declared evidence and chart artifacts. `state.json` is runtime-owned: do not read, write, or infer domain data from it.

`workflow_input.prompt_scope.product_type_request_list` is ordered. Process each requested product completely before the next one. Derive the applicable `search_sex` branches semantically from the shared product-search contract; Python does not classify products or sexes.

